  <name>FeedFlow</name>
  <summary>A minimalistic RSS Reader</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      FeedFlow is a minimalistic RSS Reader that provides a clean and simple way to read your favorite RSS feeds.
      The application is designed to open the original website for each article, allowing you to choose your preferred browser on mobile platforms.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Minimalistic and clean interface</li>
      <li>Full OPML import and export support for easy migration</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Android, iOS, macOS, Windows, Linux)</li>
      <li>Built with modern technologies (Jetpack Compose, Kotlin Multiplatform)</li>
      <li>Privacy-focused reading experience</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
